Package: OrnAtlas
Title: Expression Atlas for Ornamental Plant Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lashika", "Meena",
           email = "your.email@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")))
Description: A species-aware expression atlas tool for ornamental and
    floricultural plants. Provides functions for importing RNA-seq count
    data, building expression atlases across tissues and developmental
    stages, differential expression analysis, and publication-quality
    visualization. Includes native support for Rosa chinensis and
    Chrysanthemum morifolium.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/lashikakarnal/OrnAtlas
BugReports: https://github.com/lashikakarnal/OrnAtlas/issues
